author: bago
msg: Renamed libspf2.LICENSES to libspf2.LICENSE (naming convention for license files).
Added automatic RAT check to the maven build / site generation.
Excluded from RAT checks the resources already taken into consideration in NOTICE.
Changed the NOTICE text to be more specific about included 3rd party files and inspiration sources.

author: jvanzyl
msg: o sketching out the embedded use of the archetype and focusing on the two tasks of generation from archetype and creation

properties for sharing information and the use the request/result pattern we have for embedding.
